ents ont l’habitude de venir nous rendre visite an aprés an, venez nous voir en Barcelona !!!\n Ideal Youth Hostel, la maison des voyageurs dans le centre ville !!!  \n  Hasta pronto en Barcelona!!!\";s:9:\"min_price\";s:5:\"11.95\";s:14:\"price_currency\";s:3:\"EUR\";s:20:\"converting_hostel_id\";s:5:\"64569\";s:15:\"converted_price\";s:5:\"11.95\";s:18:\"converted_currency\";s:3:\"EUR\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":20:{s:10:\"API_booked\";s:2:\"HW\";s:14:\"site_domain_id\";s:2:\"24\";s:11:\"site_domain\";s:26:\"www.aubergesdejeunesse.com\";s:13:\"property_city\";s:9:\"Amsterdam\";s:16:\"property_country\";s:11:\"Netherlands\";s:15:\"translated_city\";s:9:\"Amsterdam\";s:18:\"translated_country\";s:8:\"Pays Bas\";s:22:\"property_booking_count\";s:2:\"16\";s:18:\"top_hostel_of_city\";s:5:\"58077\";s:15:\"property_number\";s:5:\"58077\";s:13:\"property_type\";s:6:\"Hostel\";s:13:\"property_name\";s:22:\"Amigo Hostel Amsterdam\";s:9:\"image_url\";s:59:\"http://images.webresint.com/images/hostels/mini_58077_1.jpg\";s:14:\"hostel_desc_en\";s:124:\"We offer free Wi-Fi, free walking tours and free maps and info. No curfew! This is an old neighbourhood with a long history.\";s:15:\"translated_desc\";N;s:9:\"min_price\";s:5:\"13.99\";s:14:\"price_currency\";s:3:\"EUR\";s:20:\"converting_hostel_id\";s:5:\"64569\";s:15:\"converted_price\";s:5:\"13.99\";s:18:\"converted_currency\";s:3:\"EUR\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":20:{s:10:\"API_booked\";s:2:\"HW\";s:14:\"site_domain_id\";s:2:\"11\";s:11:\"site_domain\";s:25:\"www.alberguesjuveniles.es\";s:13:\"property_city\";s:6:\"Berlin\";s:16:\"property_country\";s:7:\"Germany\";s:15:\"translated_city\";s:6:\"Berlin\";s:18:\"translated_country\";s:9:\"Allemagne\";s:22:\"property_booking_count\";s:2:\"13\";s:18:\"top_hostel_of_city\";s:5:\"14552\";s:15:\"property_number\";s:5:\"14552\";s:13:\"property_type\";s:6:\"Hostel\";s:13:\"property_name\";s:18:\"Schlafmeile Hostel\";s:9:\"image_url\";s:59:\"http://images.webresint.com/images/hostels/mini_14